#faq-info.container
  #faq-accordion.panel-group aria-multiselectable="true" role="tablist" 
    .panel.panel-default
      #headingOne.panel-heading role="tab" 
        .container
          .row.row-eq-height.vertical-align
            .col-xs-10.col-sm-10.col-md-10.col-lg-10.text-left
              h1
                | How does HYVE work?
            .col-xs-2.col-sm-2.col-md-2.col-lg-2.text-centered
              h2
                a aria-controls="collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" data-parent="" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseOne"
                  = image_tag "accordion/down.png", class: "accordion-down-arrow", html: { "aria-hidden" => "true" }

      #collapseOne.panel-collapse.collapse aria-labelledby="headingOne" role="tabpanel" 
        .panel-body
          .container
            p HYVE tags use Low Energy Bluetooth Frequency to send out information on their whereabouts to the app on your smartphone. Data sent and received will depend on the functions you select. Click here to learn more about the different functions.
    .panel.panel-default
      #headingTwo.panel-heading role="tab" 
        .container
          .row.row-eq-height.vertical-align
            .col-xs-10.col-sm-10.col-md-10.col-lg-10.text-left
              h1
                | How often do I need to replace the battery?
            .col-xs-2.col-sm-2.col-md-2.col-lg-2.text-centered
              h2
                a aria-controls="collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" data-parent="" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseTwo"
                  = image_tag "accordion/down.png", class: "accordion-down-arrow", html: { "aria-hidden" => "true" }

      #collapseTwo.panel-collapse.collapse aria-labelledby="headingTwo" role="tabpanel" 
        .panel-body
          .container
            p HYVE tags use lithium ion batteries that are rechargeable via micro-USB, so you never have to replace the batteries! The best part? Your smartphone app displays how much charge there is left in each tag. Just plug it in, charge, and use! 

