    .panel.panel-default
      #headingFive.panel-heading role="tab" 
        .container
          .row.row-eq-height.vertical-align
            .col-xs-10.col-sm-10.col-md-10.col-lg-10.text-left
              h1
                | What happens if my HYVE tag goes out of the Bluetooth range?
            .col-xs-2.col-sm-2.col-md-2.col-lg-2.text-centered
              h2
                a aria-controls="collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" data-parent="" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseFive"
                  = image_tag "accordion/down.png", class: "accordion-down-arrow", html: { "aria-hidden" => "true" }

      #collapseFive.panel-collapse.collapse aria-labelledby="headingFive" role="tabpanel" 
        .panel-body
          .container
            p When tags are further than 100ft away and do not appear on your Finder range, use the ‘Mark as Lost’ and the Mesh Network of other HYVE users will help discreetly search for your missing item, sending you a GPS location once found. Click here to understand more about the Mark as Lost function. 

    .panel.panel-default
      #headingSix.panel-heading role="tab" 
        .container
          .row.row-eq-height.vertical-align
            .col-xs-10.col-sm-10.col-md-10.col-lg-10.text-left
              h1
                | Can I share my HYVE tags with my family members/friends?
            .col-xs-2.col-sm-2.col-md-2.col-lg-2.text-centered
              h2.panel-title.blue
                a aria-controls="collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" data-parent="" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseSix"
                  = image_tag "accordion/down.png", class: "accordion-down-arrow", html: { "aria-hidden" => "true" }


      #collapseSix.panel-collapse.collapse aria-labelledby="headingSix" role="tabpanel" 
        .panel-body
          .container
            p The HYVE app is free to download on the App Store and you can purchase (bundle/bulk) promos and give some of them to your family members or friends. Unfortunately, each tag can only be paired to one phone at a time. However, you can share your tag’s unique ID with friends and family who have the app, so they can search for these items. Click here to find out more. 

