      #collapseSeven.panel-collapse.collapse aria-labelledby="headingSeven" role="tabpanel" 
        .panel-body
          .container
            p If you’ve misplaced your phone, simply click on the button on any of your paired tags and your phone will ring, allowing you to find it easily. Additionally, you can use the Sting function to leash your phone and your tags to each other, so you won’t lose your phone in the first place! Click here to find out more about Sting and other Hyve functions. 

